Revision history for TUI::Vision

2.0.1  2026-05-12
    - Rebranding and consolidation under the TUI::Vision naming.
    - Major dialog work, including StdDlg updates.
    - Documentation updates and release preparation.

2.0.0  2026-04-16
    - Initial namespace reservation for TUI::Vision
    - Added stub modules for all TUI::* components
    - Added toolkit placeholder

0.2.6  2026-04-15
    - Extended views/widgets (including text, scroll, terminal and utility
      views) with broader test coverage.

0.2.5  2025-12-31
    - Strong focus on window/menu/statusline UI components.
    - Continued API cleanup and internal refactoring across core modules.
    - More tests and assertions added for stability.
    - Documentation and structure maintenance throughout the year.

0.2.4  2024-12-31
    - Namespace/module structure migration and cleanup.
    - Core desktop/app/view building blocks expanded.
    - Geometry/toolkit foundations (point/rect/toolkit paths) matured.
    - Test and project layout improvements (including xt coverage).

0.2.3  2023-04-30
    - Repository on Github

0.2.1  2021-06-02
    - Initial release
